-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-20/clairmont-s-franz-jonathan-miller-discuss-housing-audio-.html
Patrick Franz, president of 
Clairmont Homes Ltd., and  Jonathan Miller , president and chief 
executive officer with Miller Samuel Inc., discuss housing 
statistics and lending regulations.  Franz and Miller talk with 
Bloomberg's Pimm Fox and Courtney Donohoe on "Taking Stock."   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 08:10
 